import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['life_expect'] = pd.to_datetime(data['life_expect'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    sns.scatterplot(x='fertility', y='life_expect', data=data)
    plt.title('What is the correlation between fertility and life expectancy?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['fertility'] = pd.to_numeric(data['fertility'], errors='coerce')
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='fertility', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['fertility'].median(), color='red', label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['fertility'].median()))
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of fertility rate across different countries?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['year', 'fertility', 'projected_fertility'])
    chart = sns.lineplot(x='year', y='fertility', data=data, label='Actual Fertility')
    chart = sns.lineplot(x='year', y='projected_fertility', data=data, label='Projected Fertility')
    chart.axhline(y=data['fertility'].median(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Median Actual Fertility: {:.2f}'.format(data['fertility'].median()))
    chart.axhline(y=data['projected_fertility'].median(), color='g', linestyle='--', label='Median Projected Fertility: {:.2f}'.format(data['projected_fertility'].median()))
    chart.set(xlabel='Year', ylabel='Fertility Rate')
    chart.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['year', 'life_expect', 'p_life_expect'])
    data = data.sort_values(by='year')
    sns.lineplot(x='year', y='life_expect', data=data, label='Actual Life Expectancy')
    sns.lineplot(x='year', y='p_life_expect', data=data, label='Projected Life Expectancy')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('How does the projected life expectancy compare to the actual life expectancy?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
